short_desc: Provides free groceries for low-income Tri-Valley residents
description: Provides free groceries for low-income, Tri-Valley residents. Food distribution hours are Monday, Tuesday, and Wednesday, 1-5pm; Thursday, 1-7pm. Serves families from Dublin, Livermore, Pleasanton and Sunol. To register, must bring anything with name and city (proof of residence in qualifying city).
